  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 15",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Jon II</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Fist_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"Fist of the First Men\">Fist of the First Men</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n166 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_7\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 7\">Jon I</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_14\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 14\">Catelyn II</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jon II</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 16\">Sansa II</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 26\">Jon III</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_15&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a> is observing <a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance</a>'s host, taking note of all the <a href=\"/index.php/Giants\" title=\"Giants\">giants</a> and mammoths that make up the army. <a href=\"/index.php/Tormund\" title=\"Tormund\">Tormund</a> is telling Jon some tall tales about himself, when the eagle that was once <a href=\"/index.php/Orell\" title=\"Orell\">Orell</a> rakes Jon's face. <a href=\"/index.php/Rattleshirt\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rattleshirt\">Rattleshirt</a> has arrived to bring Jon before Mance, this time at the <a href=\"/index.php/Fist_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"Fist of the First Men\">Fist of the First Men</a>. The king confronts Jon about how many men were at the Fist, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">who</a> led. Jon, seeing how many of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Watch</a> died here and realizing Mance may kill him for lying, tells the truth. The situation is still tense. Jon feels that Mance may still have him killed because Jon lied to him previously. Briefly he thinks about attacking Mance but <a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> saves him by telling them that they are lovers. The <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a> respect any man who steals his woman, and Rayder informs Jon that he will be leaving with <a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a> on the morrow to climb the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>. That night, Jon and Ygritte share a bed together.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_15&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance Rayder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tormund\" title=\"Tormund\">Tormund</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Orell\" title=\"Orell\">Orell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rattleshirt\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rattleshirt\">Rattleshirt</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Jeor Mormont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a></li></ul>\n</div>\t\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_15&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Giants\" title=\"Giants\">Giants</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fist_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"Fist of the First Men\">Fist of the First Men</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">Wildlings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_15&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from AOL member vbkorik27 previously at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a>.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2012/11/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-9\">Summary and analysis</a> of the chapter upon a first read, by Leigh Butler</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.nl/2013/01/re-read-jon-ii-membership-required.html\">Re-read: Jon II, Membership requiered</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404014139\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.061 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.231 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 242/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1104/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7686/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1138/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.38 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  214.146      1 -total\n 99.20%  212.432      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_ASoS\n 98.86%  211.704      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 98.54%  211.017      1 Template:Infobox\n  0.65%    1.390      2 Template:Columns\n  0.57%    1.229      2 Template:Work_color\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idh